The bedrock script that Hebrew, Greek, Arabic, and Latin all descend from. These are the original pictographs — the ox itself, the house itself, the water itself — not a descendant's reading of them. Rendering may require the Noto Sans Phoenician font for the pictographs to display correctly across platforms.

